{"type":"message","id":"e55c5ff4","parentId":"88d9b9c5","timestamp":"2026-04-02T01:19:38.485Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"查询结果显示只有当前这个cron任务会话，更新时间是2026-04-02 01:19:26 UTC，也就是刚才（2026-04-02 09:19 UTC+8）。这个会话是定时任务本身，不是用户发起的活跃对话。\n\n我需要检查是否有其他用户会话。查询结果显示count=1，只有一个会话就是这个cron任务本身。这意味着没有真实的用户对话在进行。\n\n但是让我再想一下，这个sessions_list查询的是我自己（agent:main）的会话。用户要求的\"活跃对话\"应该是指有真实用户消息的会话，而不仅仅是agent自己的会话。\n\n从结果来看，只有1个会话，就是当前cron任务本身发出的请求。这说明没有用户的活跃对话。\n\n按照任务要求，我应该执行自主学习：\n1. 搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态\n2. 整理3-5条关键信息\n3. 保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\n让我先读取web-search skill来了解如何搜索。","thinkingSignature":"42be1359aa7c9098b9682b24415ece3c024c5494e38609f2d2cecf5d28bfab52"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到只有当前cron任务会话，没有真实用户活跃对话。开始执行自主学习。\n\n首先读取搜索技能文件：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_10zog4yamrf9_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":820,"output":282,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45083,"cost":{"input":0.00024599999999999996,"output":0.0003384,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0019038299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775092771080}}
{"type":"message","id":"1bdf3675","parentId":"e55c5ff4","timestamp":"2026-04-02T01:19:38.491Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_10zog4yamrf9_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775092778488}}
{"type":"message","id":"ef6fa0ef","parentId":"1bdf3675","timestamp":"2026-04-02T01:19:44.706Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我了解了搜索工具的使用方法。让我搜索道简网络相关行业的最新动态。我需要搜索以下几个关键词：\n1. 企业数字化转型最新动态\n2. 智能安防行业动态\n3. 网络系统集成行业动态\n4. IT运维服务行业动态\n\n让我并行执行多个搜索来获取信息。","thinkingSignature":"95d7dff74ba7f48093a49800745da3bc786ead0089cde9dbc1cb36c7cf79715a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_v0j6gd8uz7nr_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026最新政策动态\" --output json","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_v0j6gd8uz7nr_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业动态 2026发展趋势\" --output json","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_v0j6gd8uz7nr_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务行业趋势 2026\" --output json","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_v0j6gd8uz7nr_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成行业动态 2026\" --output json","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1617,"output":272,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45870,"cost":{"input":0.0004851,"output":0.00032639999999999996,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0021309299999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775092778490}}
